narratives.question_text: Please evaluate the instructor of this course. What are the instructor's strengths and weaknesses, and in what ways might his or her teaching be improved?
comments: Instructor: Denise Esserman  She did not take the course seriously. Forgot to post links of assignments. Seldom talked about criteria before assignments.
Instructor: Michael John Kane  The worst instructor I have ever had. He did not take the course seriously. He had no plan for this course. The only thing he did was attending.
Instructor: Peter Natale Peduzzi  Dr. Peduzzi is a nice person but obviously he was so busy that did not pay any attention on this course.

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize this course for a fellow student? Would you recommend it to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I will never recommend it to other students. It is a waste of time. Sadly there is nothing can be learnt from the course.
Not very useful unless you have experience
